<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,email=no">
<meta name="full-screen" content="yes">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
<title>歌咏赛</title>
<!-- build:css({singcontest,.tmp}) styles/main.css -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/main.css" type="text/css">
<!-- endbuild -->
<script>
  var gConfig = {
    path: location.origin + '/'
  }
</script>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <div class="logo">
    <img src="images/che-icon.png" alt="">
    <img src="images/song-icon.png" alt="">
  </div>
</header>
<div class="container">
  <div class="sec">
    <section class="page1">
      <div class="body-bg">
        <img src="images/index-p-one-bg.jpg" alt="">
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="page2">
      <div class="body-bg">
        <img src="images/index-p-two-bg.jpg" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="l-t">
        <p>寻找中国“卡车人”好声音</p>
        <p>让千万“卡哥、卡嫂”亮嗓唱出心声！</p>
      </div>
      <div class="r-b">
        <p>比赛冠军将获得<img src="images/num.png" alt="">万代言费，</p>
        <p>并有机会代表“卡车人”登上</p>
        <p class="yellow">2016央视春晚舞台</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="page3">
      <div class="body-bg">
        <img src="images/index-p-thr-bg.jpg" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>比赛分为：初赛+总决赛</h2>
        <p>初赛：如下3种方式均可参加初赛</p>
        <ul>
          <li>①.参赛选手通过“车旺杯——哥·勇·赛”赛事APP录唱并上传参赛作品；</li>
          <li>②.全国36个城市举办的歌赛“路演卡车KTV”活动现场演唱。</li>
          <li>总决赛：将在初赛中评选出全国12强登上总决赛舞台进行最后的PK，由大众评委及专业评委评选出冠、亚、季军。</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="page4">
      <div class="body-bg">
        <img src="images/index-p-fou-bg.jpg" alt="" />
      </div>
      <div class="p4-con">
        <div class="tit-img">
          <img src="images/index-tit.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="app-pad20"></div>
        <div id="attention" class="download btn" data-href="">
          关注车旺微信
        </div>
        <div id="share" class="share btn" data-href="a">
          分享到朋友圈
        </div>
        <p class="tips f12">“车旺”微信报名即送500元大礼包，<br/>
前200名再送100M流量</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
  
<em class="arrow-left">
  <img src="images/arrow-left.png" />
</em>
<em class="arrow-right">
  <img src="images/arrow-right.png" />
</em>
<!-- 首页蒙层 -->
</div>
<!--上下滚动 end-->

